{"tid":2322841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠兩個星期就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-12T16:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:23:53.000Z","uid":370062,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6574e74046dc841238ebffb44381bba564be4a53","tid":2322841,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4979cb054d3723406698a74d9cbd741dcfab0466","tid":2322841,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"noted<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35612f203beed0f9b897dd8f1dcffe3f80088f2b","tid":2322841,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4979cb054d3723406698a74d9cbd741dcfab0466","tid":2322841,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"noted<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876e7f0d1364d5537cb631cae2faf7148f9c89ea","tid":2322841,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"日經post？"},{"pid":"140cfd466f30fd63781ce412da5e3424cf37bab5","tid":2322841,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"876e7f0d13